<plot>Sometime in the near future, humankind will return to the Moon to build a permanent base, as part of NASA's New Vision for Space Exploration. These modern-day pioneers will face untold dangers and endure hardships to build a new frontier for humanity in space. 'Postcards From The Future' follows the life of one man - civilian electrical engineer Sean Everman. Entrusted with the task of helping to build out the power grid on the Moonbase, Sean occasionally sends "Video Postcards" to his wife back on Earth, sharing with her the details, trials and tribulations of his job. Over the epic course of the story, these postcards from our possible future reveal the grand adventure that we are about to embark on..</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?440562</url></doc>
